      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty in person. I have absolutely babied this car, and it\u2019s still in such pristine, 'like-new' condition that it practically sparkles. It drives like an absolute dream and has been kept tucked away safely whenever it wasn't on the road. If you're looking for a ride that feels fresh off the lot without the brand-new price tag, this is definitely the one for you! Let's get you behind the wheel!",
