    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a true collector-grade specimen that defines the term 'mint.' This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, showing zero signs of road wear, paint chips, or imperfections. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating, while the factory wheels remain entirely free of curb rash. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the premium leather upholstery is supple with no bolster wear, and the original floor mats are pristine. Every switch, dial, and digital interface functions with tactile precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, featuring a comprehensive service history exclusively from authorized technicians. It has never seen rain or snow, and the undercarriage is as clean as the bodywork. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a showroom-quality vehicle that has been maintained to the highest possible standard. Complete with all original keys, manuals, and a clean title.",
      "price": 44800.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
