    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to the most exacting standards and preserved in showroom condition. This unit represents the pinnacle of its class, featuring an immaculate exterior and a pristine, smoke-free interior that reflects a history of meticulous stewardship. Engineered for the driver who demands unrivaled quality and performance, this vehicle has undergone a rigorous inspection to ensure it meets our premier mechanical benchmarks. Experience the distinction of a truly superior automobile.",
      "price": 46500.0,
