      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, you won't find a cleaner ride than this beauty. It has been absolutely pampered and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014not a single scratch or speck of dust anywhere! It's such a dream to drive, and I've taken care of it like it was my own child. You've got to see it in person to believe how perfect it is. Come take it for a spin, you're going to fall in love!",
      "price": 43500.0,
