    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a peerless example of the high-revving S54 platform, featuring a 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and a 11.5:1 compression ratio. Power is delivered through a precise ZF 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock. This specimen is mechanically flawless, with documented double-VANOS servicing, rod bearing replacement, and rear subframe reinforcement already completed to exceed factory standards. The suspension maintains its original geometry with fresh bushings and Bilstein dampers, ensuring the legendary 50/50 weight distribution remains communicative. Finished in immaculate Carbon Black, the exterior shows no signs of oxidation or road rash, while the undercarriage remains dry and free of corrosion. This is a collector-grade vehicle optimized for both the track-inclined purist and the concours enthusiast.",
